org.deeplearning4j.word2vec.sentenceiterator

Interface SentenceIterator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseSentenceIterator, CollectionSentenceIterator, FileSentenceIterator, LineSentenceIterator, UimaSentenceIterator

    public interface SentenceIterator
    A sentence iterator that knows how to iterate over sentence. This can be used in conjunction with more advanced NLP techniques to clearly separate sentences out, or be simpler when as much complexity is not needed.
